2. cs.RO (Robotics) - The paper discusses the integration of planning and execution, which is relevant to robotics. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper mentions the use of heuristic functions, which are often learned through machine learning techniques. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses planning and execution in stochastic domains, which is relevant to systems and control. 
5. cs.PL (Programming Languages) - The paper discusses the construction of plans, which is relevant to programming languages and their semantics.
